h=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Day System: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Day system is a significant addition to the game. It plays a crucial role in influencing events and interactions. When your character sleeps or certain in-game events occur, the day may change. Additionally, some character meetings and quests will now require you to be in the right location on the correct day, adding a new layer of realism and strategy to your gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras/8333e126e8e6ddf51263a9c7f70de313.avif?t=1774188236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras_big/8333e126e8e6ddf51263a9c7f70de313.avif?t=1774188236 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time System: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our Time system is another exciting feature that adds depth to your gaming experience. Time will now pass as you progress through the game and encounter various events. This dynamic element will impact how you approach challenges and decisions, making the game world feel more alive and responsive to your actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras/b98d0ac28e4e0c664262ac44d656f346.avif?t=1774188236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras_big/b98d0ac28e4e0c664262ac44d656f346.avif?t=1774188236 width=800 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint System (Improvement) :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've significantly upgraded the quest system, making it easier for players to complete quests. The hint system has also been overhauled to be clearer, more understandable, and more player-friendly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras/e93ddcb0ce8ed572f6f6080269f7cf8a.avif?t=1774188236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/extras_big/e93ddcb0ce8ed572f6f6080269f7cf8a.avif?t=1774188236 width=800 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Inventory system has been added in this update. It will now provide you with a clear view of the items you possess. This will be especially useful when you need to use specific items to complete quests or overcome obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "This game is an adult visual novel and dating sim where you manage your grandfather's apartment, experiencing strange events and building relationships with tenants. Features include a gallery system, cheat codes, fast travel, day/time mechanics, inventory, and multi-language support.", "supported_languages": "English, Thai", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/3b36793f178aaa69ec6cb20e8d0df0fbb2c4bdfc/header.jpg?t=1774188236", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/528dff49790e5ca5f720186f8217630d22c34290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1774188236", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201440/528dff49790e5ca5f720186f8217630d22c34290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1774188236", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7 or higher<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 or DirectX 9.0c compatible<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 9.0<br></li><li